{"word":"G2818 - κληρονόμος - klēronómos - klay-ron-om'-os - Heir","slug":"G2818","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κληρονόμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>klēronómos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>klay-ron-om'-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Heir"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - kle&#x0304;ronomos</b> - <i>klay-ron-om'-os</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2819\">G2819</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a> (in its original sense of <i>partitioning</i>, that is, [reflexively] <i>getting</i> by apportionment); a <i>sharer by lot</i>, that is, an <i>inheritor</i> (literally or figuratively); by implication a <i>possessor:</i> - heir."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2624\">G2624</a>, <a href=\"#/G2816\">G2816</a>, <a href=\"#/G2817\">G2817</a>, <a href=\"#/G2819\">G2819</a>, <a href=\"#/G2820\">G2820</a>, <a href=\"#/G3647\">G3647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3648\">G3648</a>, <a href=\"#/G4345\">G4345</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789\">G4789</a>"}]}